'''Alagh Rorncaurak''', or the '''Battlecavern of Unquenched Valor''', was both a chasm and a temple of [[Clangeddin Silverbeard|Clangeddin Silverbeard, the Father of Battle]], in the [[shield dwarf|dwarven]] city of [[Earthfast]], deep below the [[Earthfast Mountains]] between [[the Vast]] and [[Impiltur]], in the [[Earthroot]] region of the [[Underdark]].
